title: The Princess Anne of Denmark's letter to the Queen
author: Anne, Queen of Great Britain, 1665-1714.
notes: Princess Anne of Denmark = the future Queen Anne of Great Britain; the Queen = Mary of Modena, consort of James II.
In this edition line 11 of text ends "other"; line 19 ends "fully".
